content: "The gunshots lasted for 10-15 minutes. It didn't stop," she said. "We just ran for our lives."

tag: html body div article div div div div section div div div span
content: Her sister, Monique Dumas, said everyone dropped to the ground as as the gunman sprayed bullets.

tag: html body div article div div div div section div div div span
content: "It seemed there was a pause in the gunfire, and the people in the yellow shirts were telling the people to 'go, go, go, go,' " she said. But "the gunfire never ended, it seemed like it went on and on and on.

content: A concertgoer told CNN affiliate KLAS that frantic concertgoers piled on top of each other, trying to get out of the shooter's line of fire.

tag: html body div article div div div div section div div div span
content: "My husband and I ran out toward our car, and there were people hiding underneath my car for cover," she said.

tag: html body div article div div div div section div div div span
content: "There was a gentleman who was shot and he said, 'Can you help me?' And so I put him in my car, and I had like six people in my car -- people without shoes, running, just to get away."
